attributes.title: Will unleash ghost.
attributes.review:
This app UNLEASHED A LITERAL GHOST IN MY HOUSE. I download the app, as any American would do. Just checking in on my ✨president🧚
Then, right when it loaded, I hear a knock.
AT.MY.DOOR.
I creep outside. Mind you it’s 1am, I’m up studying US corruption and greed👼. I think this ghost of Donald trump tuned into my ~educated vibes~ and knocked to try to get me to stop informing myself.
So back to the story. I creep to the door and there’s a LITERAL GHOST. It looks JUST LIKE TRUMP- pasty but orange as well- so unique, I KNEW it was him. So in the end, DO NOT download this app, your own safety depends on it.
